      "chapterUid": 93,
      "range": "1227-1275",
      "markText": "“胡扯！你们没有结婚，我就有机会。我的老婆被你害死了，就算你还我一个。”父亲强势的性格始终未改。",
      "totalCount": 690,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300091048&chapterUid=93&rangeStart=1227&rangeEnd=1275",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/56c328f0813ab8a10g018d12?chapterUid=93&rangeStart=1227&rangeEnd=1275"
